pan=\"2\"| Certifications\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album or EP\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\" | [[FIMI|ITA]]<br/><ref name=\"Italian FIMI Charts\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.fimi.it/ricerca#/type:artists/show:charts/keyword:Maneskin/page:0|publisher=[[Federation of the Italian Music Industry]]|language=Italian|title=Database Top of the Music - Maneskin - Classifiche|accessdate=5 October 2018}}\n</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Chosen\"\n| 2017\n| 2\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|\n* FIMI: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"FIMI Certifications\">{{Cite certification|region=Italy|type=single|artist=Maneskin}}</ref>\n|''Chosen''\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Morir\u00f2 da re\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2018\n| 2\n|\n* FIMI: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"FIMI Certifications\"/>\n|rowspan=\"2\"|''Il ballo della vita''\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"Torna a casa\"\n| 1\n|\n* FIMI: 4\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"FIMI Certifications\"/>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Filmography==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" \n|-\n|+List of films featuring M\u00e5neskin\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Role\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n! class=\"unsortable\" | {{abbr|Ref.|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''This is M\u00e5neskin''\n| Themselves\n| Documentary\n| <ref name=\"This is Maneskin\"/>\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n{{X Factor (Italy)}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:X Factor (Italian TV series) contestants]]\n[[Category:Musical groups from Rome]]\n[[Category:Musical quartets]]\n[[Category:Musical groups established in 2016]]\n[[Category:2016 establishments in Italy]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox musical artist <!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject Musicians -->\n| name             = M\u00e5neskin\n| background       = group_or_band\n| image            = M\u00e5neskin, Damiano David (26476122497).jpg\n| image_size       = \n| landscape        = yes\n| caption          = M\u00e5neskin's frontman, Damiano David, performing with the band in Rome on 7 April 2018\n| origin           = [[Rome]], Italy\n| genre            = [[Pop rock]]\n| years_active     = 2015\u2013present\n| label            = {{flatlist|\n* [[Sony Music]]\n}}\n| associated_acts  = \n| website          = \n| current_members  = \n* Damiano David \n* Victoria De Angelis\n* Thomas Raggi \n* Ethan Torchio\n}}\n\n'''M\u00e5neskin''' ({{IPA-it|\u02c8m\u0254\u02d0neskin}},<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://youtube.com/watch?v=4HU0HVIH3lE|author=[[X Factor\u00a0(Italian TV series)|''X Factor Italia'']]|title=I M\u00e5neskin in collegamento dal Polo Nord {{!}} Videodiario 7|language=it|date=December 6, 2017|work=[[YouTube]]|accessdate=January 10, 2019}}</ref> {{IPA-da|\u02c8m\u0254\u02d0n\u0259\u02ccsken\u02c0|lang}};<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ordnet.dk/ddo/ordbog?query=m\u00e5neskin|title=m\u00e5neskin|language=da|work=Den Danske Ordbog|accessdate=January 10, 2019}}</ref> {{langnf||Danish|\"[[moonlight|moonshine]]\"}}) is an Italian [[pop rock]] band from [[Rome]], consisting of lead vocalist Damiano David, bassist Victoria De Angelis, guitarist Thomas Raggi, and drummer Ethan Torchio.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.it/artista/maneskin/|work=[[Rolling Stone (magazine)|Rolling Stone]]|language=Italian|title=M\u00e5neskin|accessdate=5 October 2018}}</ref>\nThe band rose to fame after ending up  second in the [[X Factor (Italy series 11)|eleventh series]] of the Italian [[talent show]] ''[[X Factor (Italian TV series)|X Factor]]'' in 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.repubblica.it/spettacoli/tv-radio/2017/12/15/news/x_factor_finale_licitra_maneskin-184165621/|title=TV X Factor, la vittoria di Lorenzo Licitra: la voce del tenore batte il glam rock dei Maneskin|work=[[la Repubblica]]|accessdate=5 October 2018|author=Luigi Bolognini|date=15 December 2017}}</ref>\n\n==History==\n===Before ''X Factor''===\nThe band members first met each other as students of the same [[Secondary education in Italy|middle school]]. In 2016, while they were students of the ''[[liceo scientifico]]'' J.F. Kennedy in [[Monteverde (Rome)|Monteverde]], [[Rome]], they decided to start a band.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://xfactor.sky.it/2017/10/19/maneskin-x-factor-2017/|publisher=[[Sky Italia]]|language=Italian|accessdate=2 November 2018|title=Maneskin|date=19 October 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"Repubblica November 2017\">{{cite web|url=https://roma.repubblica.it/cronaca/2017/11/26/news/ciclone_maneskin_il_rock_e_coatto_semo_de_roma_-182182693/|work=[[la Repubblica]]|language=Italian|accessdate=2 November 2018|title=Ciclone Maneskin, il rock \u00e8 coatto: Semo de Roma|date=26 November 2017|author=Alessandra Paolini}}</ref> \nThe band's name was chosen when they had to register for Pulse, a local music contest for emerging bands.<ref name=\"La lettura\">{{cite web|url=https://www.pressreader.com/italy/corriere-della-sera-la-lettura/20171231/281986082934933|work=[[Corriere della Sera]]. La Lettura|author=Paolo Giordano|date=31 December 2017|accessdate=2 November 2018|language=Italian|title=Ehi rag\u00e0, seguite voi stessi}}</ref> While brainstorming, Victoria, who is of Danish descent, was asked by her bandmates to toss out some Danish words, and they agreed on {{lang|da|M\u00e5neskin}} (\"moonshine\"), although its meaning is not related to the band itself.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://xfactor.sky.it/2017/12/12/maneskin-non-moleskine-x-factor-2017/|publisher=[[Sky Italia]]|language=Italian|title=Si dice Maneskin, non Moleskine!: origine e significato del nome della band|date=12 December 2017}}</ref>\nThe Pulse Contest also marked a turning point in their career, since they had to start writing their own songs. The competition led them to perform at the Felt Music Club & School, and they later went on to win first prize.<ref name=\"La lettura\"/><ref name=\"Corriere December 2017\">{{cite web|url=https://www.corriere.it/la-lettura/cards/i-maneskin-l-altra-sorpresa-x-factor/gli-esordi.shtml|work=[[Corriere della Sera]]|language=Italian|title=M\u00e5neskin, gli altri vincitori di X Factor|author=Jessica Chia|date=31 December 2017|accessdate=2 November 2018}}</ref>\n\nThey later performed as [[buskers]] in the streets of the Colli Portuensi district of Rome, as well as in the historical centre of Rome, including in [[Via del Corso]].<ref name=\"Repubblica November 2017\"/> One of their first live concerts outside their native city took place in [[Faenza]], at the 2016 Meeting of Independent Record Labels. Approximately 30 people attended the show.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ravennatoday.it/social/i-maneskin-a-faenza-sul-palco-del-mei-suonarono-di-fronte-a-non-piu-di-30-persone.html|work=Ravenna Today|language=Italian|title=I M\u00e5neskin a Faenza sul palco del Mei: Suonarono di fronte a non pi\u00f9 di 30 persone|date=10 January 2018}}</ref> After a trip in Denmark, during which the band also performed some live shows, M\u00e5neskin strengthened their cohesiveness, and started to play together for several hours a day.<ref name=\"Corriere December 2017\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rockol.it/news-683196/damiano-maneskin-si-racconta-pelliccia-come-mick-jagger|publisher=Rockol.it|language=Italian|title=Damiano (Maneskin) si racconta: \u2018Chi sono per dirmi che non posso andare in giro con la pelliccia di leopardo perch\u00e9 non sono Mick Jagger?\u2019|date=31 December 2017|accessdate=2 November 2018}}</ref>\n\n===Breakthrough===\nTheir debut single, \"Chosen\", was released on 24 November 2017 by Sony Music and charted at number 2 on the Italian [[FIMI]] Singles Chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://radiodate.it/radio-date/maneskin-chosen-177082-24-11-2017-radiodate/|publisher=Radiodate.it|language=Italian|title=Chosen - M\u00e5neskin}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://italiancharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=M%E5neskin&titel=Chosen&cat=s|publisher=Italiancharts.com. Hung Medien|title=Italina Charts - M\u00e5neskin - Songs}}</ref> It was included in the [[extended play]] of the same title, released in mid December 2017 and mainly consisting of covers previously performed during the ''X Factor'' live shows.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.repubblica.it/spettacoli/musica/2018/01/29/news/webnotte_maneskin-187582095/|work=[[la Repubblica]]|date=29 January 2018|accessdate=5 October 2018|title=L'APPUNTAMENTO Maneskin, per loro uno Speciale Webnotte: la band e un successo che non si ferma pi\u00f9|author=Alessandra Vitali}}</ref> The EP was certified platinum by the Federation of the Italian Music Industry.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ilmattino.it/spettacoli/musica/maneskin_moriro_da_re_e_il_primo_inedito_in_italiano-3616309.html|work=Il Mattino|language=Italian|accessdate=5 October 2018|title=Maneskin, \"Morir\u00f2 da re\" \u00e8 il primo inedito in italiano|date=19 March 2018}}</ref>\n\nOn 23 March 2018, the band released their first Italian-language single, \"Morir\u00f2 da re\", which continued their commercial success.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sorrisi.com/musica/dischi-in-uscita/maneskin-scelgono-la-parte-buona-moriro-da-re-il-nuovo-singolo-e-il-video/|work=[[TV Sorrisi e Canzoni]]|language=Italian|accessdate=5 October 2018|title=I Maneskin scelgono la parte buona: \"Morir\u00f2 da re\", il nuovo singolo e il video|author=Valentina Cesarini|date=22 March 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.optimaitalia.com/blog/2018/09/25/fimi-awards-per-maneskin-elisa-sfera-ebbasta-e-molti-altri-le-certificazioni-della-settimana/1228949|publisher=Optimaitalia.com|date=25 September 2018|title=Fimi Awards per Maneskin, Elisa, Sfera Ebbasta e molti altri: le certificazioni della settimana|author=Cinzia Del Pretee|accessdate=5 October 2018}}</ref> M\u00e5neskin's first full-length studio audio, featuring \"Morir\u00f2 da re\" and preceded by the ballad single \"Torna a casa\", was released on 26 October 2018.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ilmessaggero.it/spettacoli/musica/maneskin_nuovo_album_il_ballo_della_vita_docufilm-4014613.html|work=[[Il Messaggero]]|language=Italian|title=Maneskin, ecco il nuovo album \"Il ballo della vita\" e un docufilm sulla loro carriera|date=3 October 2018|accessdate=5 October 2018}}</ref> Both the album, titled ''Il ballo della vita'', and the single \"Torna a casa\" topped the charts in Italy.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.optimaitalia.com/blog/2018/11/02/fimi/1267306|work=Optimagazine|title=Nella Classifica FIMI del 2 novembre i Maneskin ed Elisa in vetta, Il Ballo Della Vita invade la Top10 dei singoli|author=Ambra De Sanctis|date=2 November 2018|accessdate=2 November 2018}}</ref>\nTo promote the album, the band theatrically released a [[documentary film]], titled ''This Is M\u00e5neskin''. The film premiered on 26 October 2018 in Italy.<ref name=\"This is Maneskin\">{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.it/cinema/news-cinema/maneskin-arriva-nei-cinema-un-documentario-che-racconta-il-primo-album-della-band/430826/|work=[[Rolling Stone (magazine)|Rolling Stone]]|language=Italian|title=M\u00e5neskin, arriva nei cinema un documentario che racconta il primo album della band|date=3 October 2018|accessdate=2 November 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Discography==\n\n===Studio albums===\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of studio albums, with chart positions and certifications\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"2\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Certifications\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\" | [[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|ITA]]<br/><ref name=\"Italian Albums Chart\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\" | [[Swiss Music Charts|SWI]]<br/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://hitparade.ch/album/Maaneskin/Il-ballo-della-vita-370510|publisher=Hitparade.ch. Hung Medien|accessdate=7 November 2018|title=M\u00e5neskin \u2013 Il ballo della vita|language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''Il ballo della vita''\n|\n* Release